  "remarks": "Qods Aeronautics Industries was listed pursuant to paragraph 12 of resolution 1737 (2006), as read with resolutions 1747, 1803 and 1929, as Iranian Revolutionary Guard Corps entities.  (Produces unmanned aerial vehicles (UAVs), parachutes, para-gliders, para-motors, etc. Iranian Revolutionary Guard Corps (IRGC) has boasted of using these products as part of its asymmetric warfare doctrine). The Director Disqualification Sanction was imposed on 09/04/2025.",
